trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of properties and values that are associated with an object in the <xref href="System.Printing"></xref> namespace.
trans-unit.target: Rappresenta una raccolta di proprietà e i valori che sono associati a un oggetto di <xref href="System.Printing"> </xref> dello spazio dei nomi.

trans-unit.source: The collection takes the form of a <xref:System.Collections.Hashtable> dictionary.
trans-unit.target: La raccolta sotto forma di un <xref:System.Collections.Hashtable>dizionario.</xref:System.Collections.Hashtable>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry.Value%2A> property of each <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry> in the collection is an instance of a class that is derived from <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty>.
trans-unit.target: La <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry.Value%2A>proprietà di ogni <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry>nella raccolta è un'istanza di una classe che deriva da <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty>.</xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty> </xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry> </xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry.Value%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inizializza una nuova istanza di <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary"></xref> class and provides it with the specified <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"></xref> and <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext>.
trans-unit.target: Inizializza una nuova istanza di <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary"> </xref> classe e fornisce l'oggetto specificato <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"> </xref> e <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext>.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext>

trans-unit.source: The data that is required to serialize or deserialize an object.
trans-unit.target: I dati necessari per serializzare o deserializzare un oggetto.

trans-unit.source: The context of the serialized stream, including the source and the destination.
trans-unit.target: Il contesto del flusso serializzato, tra cui l'origine e destinazione.

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified object (of a class that is derived from <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty"></xref>) into the dictionary.
trans-unit.target: Aggiunge l'oggetto specificato (di una classe derivata da <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty"> </xref>) nel dizionario.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty.Name%2A> property of `attributeValue` becomes the <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry.Key%2A> property of the new <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry>.
trans-unit.target: Il <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty.Name%2A>proprietà di `attributeValue` diventa la <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry.Key%2A>proprietà di nuovo <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry>.</xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry> </xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry.Key%2A> </xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty.Name%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty> as a whole becomes the <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry.Value%2A> property of the new <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty>Nel suo complesso diventa la <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry.Value%2A>proprietà di nuovo <xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry>.</xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry> </xref:System.Collections.DictionaryEntry.Value%2A> </xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty>

trans-unit.source: For another way to add an entry to the dictionary, see <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.SetProperty%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Per un altro modo aggiungere una voce al dizionario, vedere <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.SetProperty%2A>.</xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.SetProperty%2A>

trans-unit.source: An object (of a class that is derived from <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty"></xref>) that represents a property of a printing system hardware or software component.
trans-unit.target: Un oggetto (di una classe derivata da <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty"> </xref>) che rappresenta una proprietà di un componente hardware o software del sistema stampa.

trans-unit.source: Releases all the resources that are being used by the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Rilascia tutte le risorse utilizzate da di <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Call Dispose when you are finished using the <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary>.
trans-unit.target: Chiamare Dispose dopo aver terminato di utilizzare <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary>.</xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary>

trans-unit.source: The Dispose method leaves the <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: Il metodo Dispose lascia il <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary>in uno stato inutilizzabile.</xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary>

trans-unit.source: After calling Dispose, you must release all references to the <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary> so that the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: Dopo aver chiamato Dispose, è necessario rilasciare tutti i riferimenti al <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary>in modo che il garbage collector di recuperare la memoria che di <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary>occupata.</xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary> </xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Per ulteriori informazioni, vedere [la pulizia di risorse non gestite](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) e [implementazione di un metodo Dispose](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Always call Dispose before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Chiamare sempre Dispose prima di rilasciare l'ultimo riferimento a <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary>.</xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources that it is using will not be freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> method of the <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary> object.
trans-unit.target: In caso contrario, le risorse in uso non vengono liberate finché il garbage collector chiama la <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>metodo il <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary>oggetto.</xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary> </xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources that are being used by the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary"></xref> and optionally releases the managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Rilascia le risorse non gestite che vengono usate dal <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary"> </xref> e facoltativamente rilascia le risorse gestite.

trans-unit.source: This method is called by the public <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.Dispose> method and the <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Questo metodo viene chiamato dal metodo pubblico <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.Dispose>metodo e <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>metodo.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> </xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.Dispose>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.Dispose> invokes the protected Dispose method with the unnamed Boolean parameter set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.Dispose>richiama il metodo Dispose protetto con il parametro booleano senza nome impostato su `true`.</xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary.Dispose>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> invokes Dispose with the parameter set to `false`.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>richiama il metodo Dispose con il parametro impostato su `false`.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: When the Boolean parameter is `true`, this method releases all the resources that are held by any managed objects that this <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary> references.
trans-unit.target: Quando il parametro booleano è `true`, questo metodo rilascia tutte le risorse utilizzate dagli oggetti gestiti da questo <xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary>riferimenti.</xref:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary>

trans-unit.source: This method invokes the `Dispose()` method of each referenced object.
trans-unit.target: Questo metodo richiama il `Dispose()` metodo di ciascun oggetto cui viene fatto riferimento.

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: Da aggiungere.

trans-unit.source: Populates a <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"></xref> with the data that is needed to serialize the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Popola un <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"> </xref> con i dati necessari per serializzare il <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintPropertyDictionary"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Stores all the data that is used to serialize the object.
trans-unit.target: Archivia tutti i dati che viene utilizzati per serializzare l'oggetto.

trans-unit.source: Describes the context of the serialized stream, including the source and the destination.
trans-unit.target: Descrive il contesto del flusso serializzato, tra cui l'origine e destinazione.

trans-unit.source: Gets the object (of a class that is derived from <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty"></xref>) that represents the specified property.
trans-unit.target: Ottiene l'oggetto (di una classe derivata da <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty"> </xref>) che rappresenta la proprietà specificata.

trans-unit.source: The `attribName` must be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: Il `attribName` deve essere digitato esattamente come il nome di determinate proprietà di un oggetto di sistema di stampa, comprese le maiuscole e minuscole.

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.QueuePort%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> object must be spelled "QueuePort", not "PrintPort", "Port", or "Queueport".
trans-unit.target: Ad esempio, il <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.QueuePort%2A>proprietà di un <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>oggetto deve essere digitato "QueuePort", non "PrintPort", "Port" o "Queueport".</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.QueuePort%2A>

trans-unit.source: The name of the property that is represented by the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Il nome della proprietà che è rappresentato dal <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: An object of a class that is derived from the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Un oggetto di una classe derivata dal <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Implements the <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.ISerializable"></xref> interface and raises the deserialization event when the deserialization is complete.
trans-unit.target: Implementa il <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.ISerializable"> </xref> l'interfaccia e genera l'evento di deserializzazione quando la deserializzazione è completa.

trans-unit.source: The source of the event.
trans-unit.target: L'origine dell'evento.

trans-unit.source: Sets the value of the specified attribute to an object of a class that is derived from <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Imposta il valore dell'attributo specificato in un oggetto di una classe derivata da <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: If the dictionary does not already contain `attribName`, `attribName` will be added and set to `attribValue`, provided that `attribName` is identical to `attribValue`.Name.
trans-unit.target: Se il dizionario contiene già `attribName`, `attribName` verrà aggiunto e impostato su `attribValue`, a condizione che `attribName` è identico a `attribValue`. Nome.

trans-unit.source: If these values are not identical, this method does nothing.
trans-unit.target: Se questi valori non sono identici, questo metodo non esegue alcuna operazione.

trans-unit.source: The name of the attribute.
trans-unit.target: Il nome dell'attributo.

trans-unit.source: An object of a type that is derived from <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Un oggetto di un tipo derivato da <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintProperty"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: attribName is already in the dictionary and it already has the value attribValue.
trans-unit.target: attribNameè già presente nel dizionario e ha già il valore attribValue.
